##
## Introduction
##
@node Introduction "Introduction"

    Tracker Hero is a musical game for the Amiga that uses MOD song files.
    It can be played with keyboard, Joystick, Dance Mat or Guitar (Using Paul
    Willingham's PS2 to Amiga adapter, PSX64) or other PS2 to Amiga adapter.

    It has been developed on an Amiga 1200 and under WinUAE using 
    Amiblitz2, Personal Paint, Protracker and some other tools.

    This version is freely distributable.

    Enjoy!

@endnode


