@node ConfigMat "Hardware configuration required"

    @{b}Tracker Hero AGA@{ub}

      Hardware configuration: An AMIGA, with a 68020 or superior, AGA
      2MB of RAM. 6MB of free harddisk space.

    @{b}Tracker Hero ECS@{ub}

      Hardware configuration: An AMIGA, with a 68020 or superior, 1MB
