##
## 1 Configuration soft
##
@node ConfigSoft "Software configuration required"

    SoftWare configuration: Kickstart 2.0 or higher. 

    The game uses a lot of chip ram, use the game only if you have at
    least 1.5MB(AGA) or 1MB(ECS) of free chip ram.
    
@endnode

