##
## 8 Song Editor
##
@node Song_Editor "Song Editor"

    First (L)oad the module, select the key instruments, click on 
    (C)alculate top score and then save the .dat file in the datas folder. 
    Copy your mod to a folder inside songs folder. You can create new 
    folders if you wish so.   

@endnode





